import {
  Table,
  Link,
  Heading
} from 'govuk-react';


import {
  useNavigate
} from "react-router-dom";

function SummaryList() {
  return ( <
    >
    <
    Heading > Profile < /Heading>

    <
    Table caption = "Profile" >
    <
    Table.Row >
    <
    Table.Cell header = "Name" > First 6 weeks < /Table.Cell> <
    Table.Cell > £109.80 per week <
    /Table.Cell> <
    Table.Cell >
    <
    Link to = "#"
    children = "change" / >
    <
    /Table.Cell> <
    /Table.Row>

    <
    Table.Row >
    <
    Table.Cell header = "Name" > First 6 weeks < /Table.Cell> <
    Table.Cell > £109.80 per week <
    /Table.Cell> <
    Table.Cell >
    <
    Link to = "#"
    children = "change" / >
    <
    /Table.Cell> <
    /Table.Row>

    <
    Table.Row >
    <
    Table.Cell >
    <
    Table.Cell header = "Name" > First 6 weeks < /Table.Cell> <
    /Table.Cell> <
    Table.Cell > £4, 282.20 <
    /Table.Cell> <
    Table.Cell >
    <
    Link to = "#"
    children = "change" / >
    <
    /Table.Cell> <
    /Table.Row> <
    /Table> <
    />
  );
}

export default SummaryList;
